\section{Experience}

    \resumeSubheading
      {Principal Global Services}{Pune, Maharashtra}
      {Software Engineer}{July, 2024 - Present}
      \resumeItemListStart
\item[\textbullet] Designed and implemented highly scalable, low-latency \textbf{RESTful microservices} and full-stack features for payment systems processing millions of transactions, leveraging loosely coupled architectures and \textbf{IaC} to improve performance, reliability, and deployment consistency.
\item[\textbullet] Automated horizontal scaling of Database read replicas around pay cycles and implemented database indexing strategies, improving query performance and reducing resource utilisation by \textbf{25-30\%}.
\item[\textbullet] Optimized application by identifying bottlenecks across the stack, improving API response times by \textbf{35\%}, enhancing Lambda functions to efficiently handle high-traffic and multi-parameter requests.
\item[\textbullet] Led end-to-end migration of RDS transactional data to Snowflake by designing AWS Glue ETL pipelines supporting historical and daily delta loads, reducing processing time by \textbf{80\% to 90\%}, eliminating legacy jobs, and achieved \textbf{100\%} data accuracy with zero downtime.
\item[\textbullet] Identified and resolved critical security vulnerabilities across frontend and backend systems, handled defect resolution end-to-end, mitigated payout risks during scheduled cycles, conducted root-cause analysis, and proactively prevented production issues.
\item \textbf{Tech used:} AWS, Java, Spring Boot, Typescript, React.js, Node.js, Microservices, REST APIs, PostgreSQL, MongoDB, Snowflake.
\resumeItemListEnd

